description: At least three sons and three grandchildren of Hamas leader Ismail Haniyeh killed on Wednesday in Israeli air attack on Gaza refugee camp, relatives and official Hamas media said.
title: Haniyeh says three of his sons killed in Israeli airstrike on Gaza

description: TEHRAN - In a speech delivered at Imam Khomeini’s Grand Mosalla in Tehran, Ayatollah Seyyed Ali Khamenei, the Leader of the Islamic Revolution, once again asserted that Israel will face consequences for its recent attack on Iran’s embassy in Damascus.
title: “Israel will be punished”

description: TEHRAN – On Wednesday, Leader of the Islamic Revolution Ayatollah Ali Khamenei told an Eid al-Fitr meeting of the country’s officials and ambassadors of Muslim states in Tehran that rallies on International Quds Day on April 5 was “surprising”.
title: Ayatollah Khamenei calls Quds Day rallies ‘surprising’

description: TEHRAN – Iran lost to Slovenia 3-2 (25-13, 11-25, 25-22, 23-25, 15-13) in a heart-stopping match on Wednesday in the 2024 WPV Sitting Volleyball Final Paralympics Qualifiers for Women final.
title: Iran’s women’s sitting volleyball fail to reach 2024 Paralympics

description: The Islamic Resistance in Iraq says it has carried out a fresh strike on an Israeli target in the occupied Palestinian territories.
title: Iraqi Islamic Resistance targets Israel’s oil port in Haifa

description: UN Secretary-General António Guterres has expressed his sorrow at the violence affecting Muslims in Gaza and elsewhere in his annual greeting for Eid al-Fitr.
title: UN chief says ‘heart is broken’ over Gaza in Eid greeting

description: TEHRAN - Leader of the Islamic Revolution Ayatollah Ali Khamenei said on Wednesday that Israel “must be punished and will be punished” for its deadly air raids on the Iranian consulate in Damascus, which is considered part of the Iranian territory.
title: Leader: Israel ‘must be punished and will be punished’ for attack on Iranian consulate
